item.description: Writing this on: January 29, 2024 03:48 Probably last week, I remember just waking up and then deciding to make a website,learnt some html css and made a crappy (somehow working) static web page. A blog to be precise because what else can you think of, then i got bored and forgot about it :P tonight when i was trying to sleep from flu,i felt like doing it no matter how dull it feels (been procrastinating this from couple years now),
